table concurrent_futures_extra133.cf_future_method_argcount:
  description: "concurrent.futures.Future method co_argcount checks in cffutqn133 namespace — wave 259 theme: Future method co_argcounts; set_result.co_argcount==2 (self + result value); set_exception.co_argcount==2 (self + exception object); running.co_argcount==1 (self only — no-arg predicate returning bool); cancel.co_argcount==1 (self only); result.co_argcount==2 (self + timeout, where timeout defaults to None); done.co_argcount==1 (self only — no-arg predicate returning bool); verified with Python 3.14.3"
